name: Moist Orange Almond Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Cover oranges with water and boil till soft, roughly about 60 minutes.
Allow oranges to cool and chop them into pieces, removing any seeds. Preheat oven to 150 degree Celsius.
Blend oranges until smooth. Add baking powder, eggs, sugar and almond meal.
Pour into a lined baking tin and bake for 60 minutes, or until when a skewer comes out clean.
